# libwallet

libwallet is a library for crypto wallet devices access from Linux, 
Android, Mac OS X, Windows, OpenBSD/NetBSD and Solaris userspace
It is written in C++ and licensed under the GNU
Lesser General Public License version 2.1 or, at your option, any later
version (see [COPYING](COPYING)).

libwallet is abstracted internally in such a way that it can hopefully
be ported to other operating systems.
